Putaway of inventory

55124 : Putaway inventory
Putaway materials from Quality Control zone

1
Execute the putaway process
1.1

On the handheld device, from the main menu, select 'INBOUND'.

1.2

Select 'PUTAWAY'.

2

Input the container code or the label for materials that are in the quality control zone

3

Select the item to putaway

4

Validate that the Information about the item is displayed, including the destination location

5

Enter the quantity to putaway
6

Scan or enter the destination location

7

Validate that a message is displayed, and that the item has been putaway successfully
